Package: ggokabeito
Title: Okabe-Ito Scales for 'ggplot2' and 'ggraph'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Malcolm", "Barrett", , "malcolmbarrett@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0299-5825"))
Description: Discrete scales for the colorblind-friendly 'Okabe-Ito'
    palette, including 'color', 'fill', 'edge_colour', and 'edge_fill'. 
    'ggokabeito' provides 'ggplot2' and 'ggraph' scales to easily use the 
    'Okabe-Ito' palette in your data visualizations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/malcolmbarrett/ggokabeito
BugReports: https://github.com/malcolmbarrett/ggokabeito/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    grDevices
Suggests: 
    ggraph,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vdiffr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
